<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>只做专场人才拍卖 - 实力拍</title>
	<meta name="keywords" content="实力拍, 人才拍卖">
	<meta name="description" content="实力拍是深圳市红领巾网络科技有限公司旗下的项目">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="renderer" content="webkit|ie-comp|ie-stand">
	<meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate">
	<meta http-equiv="Pragma" content="no-cache">
	<meta http-equiv="Expires" content="0">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="../css/img/logo_ico.ico">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/common/normalize.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/common/global.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/common/vip.css">
	
	<!-- <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/dist/master.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/dist/vip.min.css"> -->
	
	<!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="./js/common/html5.min.js"></script>
      <script src="./js/common/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
    
	<script src="../js/common/require_config.js" defer="true"></script>
	<script data-main="../js/controller/vip" src="../js/common/require.min.js" defer="true"></script>
	<!-- <script type="text/javascript" src="../js/controller/dist/vip-built.min.js" defer="true"></script> -->
</head>
<body>
	<div class="viewport">
		<div id="header" ng-include src="'../views/header.html'" ng-controller="headerCtrl" ng-init="getUserInfo()"></div>
		<div id="main" ng-controller="vipCtrl">
			<div class="plus-wrap">
				<div class="seats">
					<div class="seats-dot">				
						<div class="seats-con">
							<div class="text">
								<span>实力拍Plus</span>
								<br/>
								<span class="seats-font">在这里，招聘从未如此高效（限50位名额立即抢购）</span> 
							</div>
							<div class="btn-group"> 
								<!-- <a class="btn btn-open" href="/base/vippool">人才邀约</a> -->
								<a class="btn btn-open" href="#" onclick="javascript:document.getElementById('footer').scrollIntoView()"></>人才邀约</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="plus-box">
					<div class="title">
						<span>什么是实力拍plus</span>
					</div>
					<div class="intro">
						<div class="tip">
							<h3>招聘，如何做的更好？实力拍 Plus给你更多的选择,在每周的定时人才拍卖之外,</h3>
							<h3>实力拍将为实力拍Plus企业提供上万个技术、运营、产品等，精英们等你</h3>
							<h3>一键激活并承诺邀约失败立即返还全额。</h3>
						</div>
						<div class="intro-con">
							<img alt="" src="../css/img/vip_bg_1.png">
							<img alt="" src="../css/img/vip_bg_2.png">
							<img alt="" src="../css/img/vip_bg_3.png">
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="title">
						<span>加入实力拍Plus</span>
					</div>
					<div class="spulist">
						<div class="spu-tr">
							<div class="spu-list">
								<div class="spu-item">
									<div class="spu-box">
										<span class="price">￥499</span>
										<span class="count">500金币10次邀约</span>
									</div>
									<div class="btn-group">
										<a class="btn btn-pay box-shadow" ng-click='jumpPay(1)' target="_blank">马上购买</a>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="spu-list">
								<div class="spu-item">
									<div class="spu-box">
										<span class="price">￥950</span>
										<span class="count">1000金币20次邀约</span>
									</div>
									<div class="btn-group">
										<a class="btn btn-pay box-shadow" ng-click='jumpPay(2)' target="_blank">马上购买</a>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="spu-list">
								<div class="spu-item">
									<div class="spu-box">
										<span class="price">￥2250</span>
										<span class="count">2500金币50次邀约</span>
									</div>
									<div class="btn-group">
										<a class="btn btn-pay box-shadow" ng-click='jumpPay(3)' target="_blank">马上购买</a>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="clear"></div>
					<div class="contact"><span>*</span>成功与候选人勾搭上才为有效邀约，候选人未回应或者拒绝的实力拍Plus将被视为无效邀约，并返还金币。</div>

					<div class="pay-modal modal">
						<div class="modal-backdrop in"></div>
						<div class="modal-dialog">
							<div class="modal-content">
								<div class="paying">
									<img src="../css/img/load.gif" alt="loading" />
									<div class="modal-body">
										<p>支付完成前，请不要关闭此支付验证窗口。</p>
										<p>支付完成后，请点击支付完成按钮跳转至会员拍卖池。</p>
										<p>如暂时无法跳转，请等待10秒后刷新本页面，进入会员拍卖池。</p>
									</div>
									<div class="paying-btn">				
									<span class="btn2" ng-click="_close('.pay-modal')">取&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;消</span><span class="btn1" ng-click="showVipPool()">支付完成</span>	
									</div>									
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>


				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="footer" ng-include src="'../views/footer.html'"></div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
